1. Installation
Device A: "pip install fastapi uvicorn pydantic speechrecognition pyttsx3 paho-mqtt 
deep-translator requests"
Device B: "pip install paho-mqtt gTTS"

2. Download "Eclipse Mosquitto" on device A

3. Go to Services -> Find "Mosquitto Broker" -> right-click on it and choose stop

4. Open a new terminal in device A and then input "mosquitto -c mosquitto.conf -v"

5. On device A, open the Command Promt and input "ipconfig", ( "ifconfig" if on Mac/Linux ), find 
the IPv4 Address and then copy it.

6. Open the codedeviceB.py on device B and replace MQTT_BROKER = "IP_ADDRESS" with IP_ADDRESS is 
the IPv4 address in step 4

7. On device A, open the terminal and enter "uvicorn local_api:app --port 7071", open another 
terminal and enter "python codedeviceA.py"

8. Open the terminal on device B and enter "python codedeviceB.py"

